snippet.title: Splatoon 3 - Salmon Run Next Wave Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The next wave of Salmon Run’s co-op action returns in Splatoon 3! But with this mysterious new giant Salmonid in the picture it might be a tougher challenge than swimming upstream! 

Splatoon 3 launches this summer, only on #NintendoSwitch. https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/splatoon-3-switch/
